Quickstrike:




Quickstrike looked at Stingtra. "No, ah don't think we do," he replied to 
her. He thought for a moment to think of what he could do for her. While 
thinking, he remembered the sporting game he and Tarantsulus played once in 
a while. He laughed. The only way it could be described as was a one-legged 
butt kicking contest. There were several times when he lost. It was due to 
that he couldn't keep his balance. Having such large feet that he had 
weren't easy with a sport like that. But when he did nail the spider, it 
hurt.
